The line of thought is to provide the exact proof term for `↑m ≤ ↑n` using the available hypothesis `hmn`. The `of_le` tactic expects a proof of this inequality.

```tactics
theorem ContMDiffAt.contMDiffAt_tangentMap (x₀ : TangentBundle I M)
    (hf : ContMDiffAt I I' n f x₀.proj) (hmn : m + 1 ≤ n) :
    ContMDiffAt I.tangent I'.tangent m (tangentMap I I' f) x₀ := by
  rw [contMDiffAt_totalSpace]
  refine ⟨(hf.comp x₀ (contMDiffAt_proj (TangentSpace I))).of_le (Nat.cast_le.mpr (Nat.le_of_succ_le hmn)), ?_⟩
```
